tadabhilāṣi tatparivārārthi.

<commentary>asahiṣṇv asahanaśīlam. alasaṃ kriyāsu akarmaṇyam, kusīdam ity arthaḥ. bhītaṃ kāyajīvitabhīru bhayahetubhyo vā. pragalbhaṃ dhṛṣṭam. mukharaṃ durvacaskam, yuktāyuktamanapekṣyābhidhāyakaṃ vā. svapakṣeḥ śiṣyāntevāsijñātisālohitādau abhiniviṣṭaṃ pakṣapātātiśayavat.</commentary>

sāṃprataṃ pratikāranirdeśam āha. upadarśitakrameṇa saṃkliṣṭaṃ saṃkleśasaṃprayuktaṃ niṣphalavyāpāraṃ vā jñātvā svacittaṃ sarvapravṛttinigedhena prabhāvamandatāṃ vidhāya nigṛhṇīyād abhibhavet.